data.description: Welcome to this remarkable home! It offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm, packed with amenities. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious living room with a cathedral ceiling and exposed wood structural beams. Sky tubes artfully bring in natural light, creating a serene atmosphere whether you're entertaining guests or relaxing by the natural gas fireplace. This home is designed for the modern world, with Ethernet ports in every room, central AC, an attic fan, and smart thermostat. The kitchen is fully equipped with a refrigerator, a GE Prestige dishwasher and oven. For eco-conscious homeowners, this home features solar panels installed in January 2022. The LG 19,140 kWh power capacity array is 11,400 kWh larger than recommended with the ability to connect to a backup power generator and batteries. Your privacy is ensured with two automated front privacy gates. The front yard boasts mature redwoods, a fig tree, pomegranate, Myrtles, and Japanese maples. The spacious back yard features an ash tree, Silky pear tree, Sweet Orange tree, Sour Orange tree, Feijoa trees, Myrtle trees, Horsehead Monstera, mint, and grapes. The custom-built wide side gate(s) provide easy access to the pool, motorcycle parking, two storage sheds and a dog run. A short drive up Palm Avenue, or a lovely walk through the Old Fig Garden neighborhood grants you access to the celebrated Christmas Tree Lane, and to the convenience of The Fig Garden Village shopping center.
